node.title: State funeral for Bert Newton to be held next Friday
node.alt: Bert Newton in a tuxedo suit waving on the Logies red carpet
node.description: Entertainer Bert Newton will be honoured with a state funeral in Melbourne next Friday, with the service to be live streamed.
node.content: ["A state funeral service for entertainer Bert Newton will be held next Friday, November 12, in Melbourne, the Victorian government has announced.", "The service will be held at St Patrick's Cathedral in East Melbourne.", "Due to COVID-19 requirements, only friends, family and colleagues will be able to attend.", "The proceedings will be live streamed.", "Newton died aged 83 last weekend.", "More to come."]
